Journey Page My Programs

Description & Requirements

Description:

You are supposed to run the WDT tester Example and assure it has the same behavior as the videos.

 

Detailed Requirements

  1. Prepare the development Environment
    1. Create a new Keil project  for the TivaC board
  2. Download Source files
    1. Add WDT tester source files
      1. wdt_driver.c
      2. wdt.h
      3. wdt_tester.c
  3. Verify the driver's functionality
    1. Make sure to get the same behavior as seen in the videos

Delivery

  1. Deliver a video where you can show that the development environment and the driver are working fine.
